You put the key into the ignition, start (8e604dac-258a-46ae-b421-44202fd18dfc)

You put the key into the ignition, start it, hold the bars with both hands and press the levers behind them to accelerate. Most jet skis do not have brakes; you simply release the levers and the force of the water will stop it fast. Jet skis are simple to operate, but it takes some time getting used to riding them. 

Also, don't make sudden turns until you gain some experience, okay?
